  "texts": [
    "First, we set the response that the Chatbot will provide when the Default Welcome Intent is recognized.",
    "This way, for all welcome messages sent by a user to F-One, the Chatbot will respond as follows: \"Hi, my name is F-One and I'm here to assist you!",
    "What do you want to know about Formula 1?\"",
    "Next, to connect the LangChain Agent to the Dialogflow Agent and enable response generation, we created a webhook.",
    "We named the webhook as \"f1-webhook.\""
  ],
